title: The Importance of a Clear Vision
itunes:title: The Importance of a Clear Vision
description:
In this episode, Rob and Dean break sown how to create a clear vision, how to figure out who you need to be to create that life and what standards you need to hold yourself to in order to make that vision a reality.
